flowRoot.flowPara: Since the first IPCC report, the scientific literature on climate change has grown exponentially. This introduces major challenges to the processing and synthesis of scientific knowledge.

A necessery step towards synthesising the growing climate change literature is to introduce more formalised systematic review methods, while taking advantage of new developments in computational linguistics and text-mining.
